node.text:
I worry about the world, the people I love, and the weird thing I said at a dinner 3 years ago. It all piles up. So, Simon pushed me to go away for a week, turn off IG, and take a deep breath. 
I found this cute little place in Sonoma @macarthurplace and took my little sister @jordiefos. 
I came home a different person. Still just as cute, just more relaxed ❤️
🎶: Parachute by John K

node.title: I struggle with a decent amount of anxiety everyday.

node.text: Don’t know about you, but I’m finding it very exhausting to be a person these days.
